parameters:
\nw[Coachman]The person you're with is resting inside the
carriage.

\nw[\N[21]]The location is around here... but it seems like
they're quite far down.

\nw[\N[3]]But this place is more like a marshland than a
lake. It's hard to imagine it becoming too deep.

\nw[\N[3]]It's strange to think that there's an underground
area in a marshland, but it might be worth
considering that possibility and exploring.

\nw[\N[21]]I see... So we're searching for an entrance to the
underground while looking for a place with deep
water.

\nw[\N[21]]Well, even if we dive underwater, it's hopeless.
We don't have any equipment to dive underwater, so
all we can do is wait for now.

\nw[\N[21]]Whatever we do, we should start with an
investigation. It would be great if there's an
entrance to the underground.

\nw[\N[3]]When you want to take a break or go shopping, talk
to the coachman.

\nw[\N[21]]Ah, Fross who can't move because her legs gave out
is also in the carriage. Let's rely on her to
recover our magical power.

\N[\V[111]] was temporarily enhanced by the
succubus' abilities. (This enhancement state will
be lifted under conditions such as being
incapacitated, fully recovering through rest, or
the passage of time.)

\nw[Thorz]Even if you have high resistance, you can still
get tired. It's a good thing I'm small and it was
tough.

\nw[Huma]The way you feel can change depending on the
position and movements. Let's try various things,
okay!
